---
layout: base.njk
title: Network Offerings
description: Electron Workshop facilitates access to open-source tools for community groups — delivered by network providers who set their own terms and share our values.
permalink: "/offering/"
---
<h1 class="mb-2">Network Offerings</h1>
<p class="text-secondary mb-1">
  Electron Workshop doesn't provide these services directly — it facilitates access to them through a network of providers who share our values.
  Each provider sets their own terms, capacity, and pricing (including pro-bono arrangements).
  Community groups choose who they engage with.
</p>
<p class="text-secondary mb-1">
  <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i>
  <strong>You don't need to be a network member to access these offerings.</strong>
  They are open to any community group or non-profit that connects with a provider directly.
  Network membership brings additional benefits — but the tools themselves are not gated.
</p>
<p class="mb-4">
  <a href="/initiatives/electron-network/" class="text-primary fw-semibold">Learn about the Electron Network →</a>
</p>

<style>
  .offering-logo{ max-height: 36px; width: auto; }
  .provider-logo{ max-height: 22px; width: auto; object-fit: contain; }
</style>

<div class="row g-4">
  {% for item in offerings %}
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <div class="card h-100 border-primary border-opacity-25 shadow-sm border-primary-hover">
        <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
          <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            {% if item.logo %}
              <img src="{{ item.logo }}" alt="{{ item.title }} logo" class="offering-logo">
            {% endif %}
            <h2 class="h5 mb-0">{{ item.title }}</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="flex-grow-1">{{ item.text }}</p>

          {% if item.providers and item.providers.length > 0 %}
            <div class="border-top pt-2 mt-2 mb-3">
              <p class="text-muted mb-2" style="font-size:.75rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.06em;">Provided by</p>
              <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3 align-items-center">
                {% for provider in item.providers %}
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-1">
                    {% if provider.logo %}
                      <img src="{{ provider.logo }}" alt="{{ provider.name }}" class="provider-logo">
                    {% else %}
                      <span class="small fw-semibold text-dark">{{ provider.name }}</span>
                    {% endif %}
                    <span class="text-muted" style="font-size:.7rem;">({{ provider.role }})</span>
                  </div>
                {% endfor %}
              </div>
            </div>
          {% endif %}

          <div>
            <a href="/offering/{{ item.slug }}/" class="stretched-link btn btn-primary" aria-label="{{ item.title }}">Read more</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<div class="mt-5 p-4 rounded border border-primary border-opacity-25 bg-light">
  <div class="row align-items-center g-3">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-8">
      <h3 class="h5 mb-1">Want to contribute to the network?</h3>
      <p class="mb-0 text-secondary">Whether you have dev capacity, can offer hosting, funding, promotional reach, or are exploring a CSR engagement — there's a path for you.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-4 text-md-end">
      <a href="/initiatives/electron-network/" class="btn btn-primary">Join the Network</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="text-center mt-4">
  <p class="mb-0 text-secondary">Questions? Email <strong>support[at]electronworkshop.com.au</strong></p>
</div>
